  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK235">
<l>nattampōṟ kēṭu muḷatākuñ cākkāṭum </l>
<l>vittakaṟ kallā laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Prosperity to the body of fame, resulting in poverty to the body of flesh and the stability to the former arising from the death of the latter, are achievable only by the wise.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
